21 United States, the several states, territories, or possessions, or the
22 District of Columbia.
23 (3)(a) Possession of a deadly weapon which is not a firearm by a
24 prohibited person is a Class III felony.
25 (b) Possession of a deadly weapon which is a firearm by a prohibited
26 person is a Class ID felony for a first offense and a Class IB felony for
27 a second or subsequent offense.
